reviewText: I PURCHASED THIS VIDEO FOR MY GRANDCHILDREN FOR THEIR SECOND BIRTHDAY AND THEY REALLY ENJOYED IT.  THEY LIKE THE LITTLE PEOPLE VERY MUCH, SO IT KEPT THEIR INTEREST.  IF YOUR UNFAMILIAR WITH THE LITTLE PEOPLE, THEY ARE VERY GENTILE AND KIND, AND THOUGHTFUL, AND HELPFUL TO ANOTHER,WHICH IS A WONDERFUL THING TO SHOW TO CHILDREN. I HAVE PURCHASED MANY OF THEIR VIDEOS AND THEY ARE OFTEN REQUESTED.
